### create patient (admin)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/patients
Authorization: Bearer 
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Dana",
  "last_name": "Akhmetova",
  "gender": "F",
  "phone": "+77077777777",
  "email": "dana@mail.local",
  "address": "Almaty",
  "comment": "new patient"
}

### list doctors (admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/doctors
Authorization: Bearer 

### create appointment (admin)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/appointments
Authorization: Bearer 
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_id": 1,
  "doctor_id": 2,
  "start_at": "2026-04-06T09:00:00Z",
  "end_at": "2026-04-06T09:30:00Z",
  "status": "SCHEDULED",
  "reason": "First consultation",
  "comment": "checkpoint demo"
}

### list doctor schedules
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctor/schedules
Authorization: Bearer 

### doctor set appointment status
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/doctor/appointments/1/status
Authorization: Bearer 
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CONFIRMED"
}
